<b>Charles Pratt and Company</b> was an oil company that was formed in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../384/47384.xml">
Brooklyn, New York</link> in the <body wordnetid="107965085" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
<political_orientation wordnetid="106212839" confidence="0.8">
<colony wordnetid="108374049" confidence="0.8">
